quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,"Mata-an! a so Alongan a Kokoman na diyandi kiran langon,-"
  44,41,"Alongan a da-a Khilinding o Tonganai ko Tonganai niyan a mai­to bo, go di siran Phangatataban­gan,"
  44,42,"Inonta so ini Kalimo o Al­lah: Mata-an! A Sukaniyan na Su­kaniyan so Mabagur, a Makalimo­on."
  44,43,"Mata-an! A so kayo a Zaq­qum,"
  44,44,"Na Pangunungkun o Bara­dosa,-"
  44,45,"Lagid o Totonagun a Ga­lang, a Pundidi ko manga Tiyan,"
  44,46,"Lagid o Kapundidi o Phuli­kabo a ig."
  44,47,"(Tharo-on:) Kowa-a niyo sukaniyan na goyoda niyo to ko Lumbak o Naraka Jahim!"
  44,48,"Oriyan niyan na ododa niyo ko Poro o Olo niyan so siksa a Phulikabo."
  44,49,"(Tharo-on non:) Ta-a min­gka! Mata-an! A suka na suka so Mabagur, a Paga-adatan (sa Do­niya)!"
  44,50,"Mata-an! A giyaya so sukano na Shasangka kano ron!"
  44,51,"Mata-an! A so Khipana­nanggila na si-i ko Darpa a sasari­gan,"
  44,52,"Si-i ko manga Pamomolan go manga Bowalan;"
  44,53,"Ndiditar siran sa Sotra a Manipis go Sotra a Makapal, a Khipaga-adapa dapa;"
  44,54,"Giyoto dun man, go Pakaphamangaroma-an Nami siran sa manga Tataid, a manga. Pipiya i Kapumata."
  44,55,"Puphananawag siran ro-o sa Pithibarang a Onga, a Khisasarig siran;"
  44,56,"Da-a khasagadan niran ro-o a Kapatai, inonta so Kapatai a Pa­ganai (sa Doniya); go Phakalidasun Niyan siran ko siksa ko Naraka Jahim,-"
  44,57,"Kakaya-an a pho-on ko Kadnan Ka! Giyoto man na Suka­niyan so Da-ag, a Mala!"
  44,58,"Na aya dun a Kiyaluboda Mi ron, si-i ko Basangka, na a niran Sabota (a Qur-an naya)."
  44,59,"Na nayao Ka; Mata-an! A siran na Nomanayao siran (mam­bo)."